        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This staff is made of a dense wood and strikes the ground with an imposing boom. At the top of the staff is a perfectly round obsidian sphere that, when stared at for too long, makes viewers feel as though they're heavier than before. When wielding this staff, you gain a +1 item bonus to saves against forced movement.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Gale Blast]</em></p>\n<p><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Air Bubble]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Gravitational Pull]</em></p>\n<p><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Gentle Breeze]</em></p>\n<p><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Gravity Well]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Tempest Cloak]</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed ranks of all listed spells.</p>"
